Package guardians.model.dtos Description

This packed will contain the DTO classes (Data Transfer Objects) used to serialize the entities of the model. These are the currently existing DTOs: Public DTOs: These DTOs will represent the REST interface. Example DoctorPublicDTO Scheduler DTOs: These DTOs will represent the interface provided to the scheduler Using the DTO pattern allows changing the fields and methods of the model entities without worrying about exposing undesired data through the different interfaces
